extends ./layout/default.jade

block variable
    - var chapter_num = "5.1"
    - var chapter_title_en = "Briefing"
    - var chapter_title_cn = "作戰指南"


block title
    title MGS #{chapter_num} - #{chapter_title_en} (#{chapter_title_cn})

block container
    h2.title.title-en
        span.title-num #{chapter_num}
        strong.title-en
            | #{chapter_title_en}
        strong.title-cn
            | #{chapter_title_cn}
    p.narration
        span.narration-en
            | This is the conversation that take place when you play the briefing.  It takes place before the actual game so i have placed it before the game script itself.  I have retrieved the order of the conversations by looking at T Huynh's Briefing Mode Guide.  I have written it out as one long conversation instead of being split up into parts.
        span.narration-cn
            | 這是在玩遊戲時會進行的對話。算遊戲的背景介紹，所以我把他放在遊戲腳本前面，我覺得這個「作戰指南」模式很有必要說一下。而且我不打算獨立拆分這部分，而是把他歸為一個小節。
    .gallery.gallery-2
        img(src="./assets/img/001.jpg", alt="")
        img(src="./assets/img/002.jpg", alt="")
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100001_It's_been_a_long_time_Snake.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | It's been a long time Snake.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 好久不見，Snake。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I should've known you were behind this, Colonel.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 我沒發現你在後面，上校。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That's no way to greet an old war buddy Snake.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 不歡迎當年戰場上的老夥計嗎？
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What do you want from me?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 你想從我這裏打聽點什麼？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I just invited you here so we could have a talk.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 只是請你過來聊聊。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Invited!? That's what you call sending armed soldiers after me?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 聊聊？這就是你對待退伍士兵的方式？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Sorry if they were a little rough with you. But we've got a serious situation here. Only you can get us out of it.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 請原諒我們的粗莽，我這邊有件急事，而且只有你能搞定。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm retired from FOX-HOUND. You're not my commander anymore, and I don't have to take orders from you or anyone else.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 我已退出FOX-HOUND，你不再是我的指揮官，我也不會再接你的任務。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You will take these orders. I know it.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 你會的。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Excuse me.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 打擾一下。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Who's this?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 是誰？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Dr. Naomi Hunter. She's chief of FOX-HOUND's medical staff and an expert in gene therapy.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Naomi Hunter 醫生。 他是FOX-HOUND的醫務人員，拿手基因治療。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Are you military?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 軍人？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | No, civilian. I've been sent here from ATGC. Pleasure to meet you
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 不，我是平民。我是ATGC派來的，很高興認識你。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Don't worry this injection won't hurt a bit.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 別擔心，這次注射不會給你帶來任何傷害。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What's the shot for?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 打什麼針？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What's wrong? You don't like shots?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 別怕，你不喜歡打針？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake listen up. It all went down five hours ago. Heavily armed soliders occupied Shadow Moses Island, a remote island off the coast of Alaska.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 聽好了Snake。 5小時後， 武裝士兵就會佔領影子摩西島，這是個位於阿拉斯加的偏遠島嶼。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What soldiers?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 這些士兵什麼來頭？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Next-Generation Special Forces led by members of unit FOX-HOUND. They've presented Washington with a single demand, and they say that if it isn't met, they'll launch a nuclear weapon.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | Next-Generation特種部隊，由FOX-HOUND成員帶領。他們已向華盛頓提出單方要求，如果得不到滿足，他們就會發射核武器。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | A nuclear weapon?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 核武器？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm afraid so. You see, the island is the site of a secret nuclear weapons disposal facility.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 恐怕是這樣，你看，這個島是個機密的核武器處理設備。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | FOX-HOUND hijacking a nuclear weapon?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | FOX-HOUND劫持了核武器？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Now you understand how serious the situation is. You'll have two mission objectives. First, you're to rescue the DARPA (Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency) Chief, Donald Anderson, and the president of ArmsTech, Kenneth Baker. They're both being held as hostages.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 現在你應該意識到問題的嚴重性了吧。你有兩個任務。首先，你要救出DARPA（美國國防部高級研究計畫局）局長，Donald Anderson，還有ArmsTech公司的總裁，Kenneth Baker。 這兩個被關押的人質。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Those are some heavy duty hostages.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 都是一些重量級地人質。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Secondly, you're to investigate whether or not the terrorists have the ability to launch a nuclear strike, and stop them if they do. Any questions, Snake?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 其次，你要調查這些恐怖份子是否能發動核打擊。如果有，就想辦法停止掉。還有什麼問題嗎，Snake。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Questions? I haven't even said whether I'd accept this mission.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 問題，我都還沒答應要這個任務。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Well you can make up your mind after you hear more about the situation.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 等你下定決心後，我們再接著說。
    .gallery.gallery-2
        img(src="./assets/img/003.jpg", alt="")
        img(src="./assets/img/004.jpg", alt="")
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100002_Tell_me_about_the_nuclear_weapon_disposal_facility.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Tell me about the nuclear weapons disposal facility.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 說一下這個核武器處理設施。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The disposal facility includes a hardened underground base. Even with our most advanced intelligence gathering equipment, we can't tell what's happening inside.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 這個處理設施包含一個堅硬的地下基地。即便我們用上最先進的設備，也無法得知那裡面發生了什麼。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So someone needs to penetrate, gather intelligence, and report back... Sounds like a spy movie. What's the insertion method?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 看起來需要潛入，獲得情報並回傳⋯⋯ 這聽起來像間諜電影。有什潛入方法了嗎？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Well an air insertion is impossible.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 從空中看來是不可能的了。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Not with this storm going on.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 不能逆風暴而行。
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | We'll approach the disposal facility by sub.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 我想可以潛入接近處理設施。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Approach?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 接近？
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes, within a few miles of it. The facility is equipped with sonar detection capability. They'd be able to hear our engine or propeller noise.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | 對，再過幾英里。
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | And then?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | We'll launch a one-man SDV (swimmer delivery vehicle).
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Launch?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Same as a torpedo. Only this has no propulsion device of its own. After the SDV gets as close as it can, dispose of it. From there on you'll have to swim.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You want me to swim in sub-zero Alaskan water?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Don't worry. That suit represents the latest advances in poly- thermal technology. The nuclear weapons disposal facility covers the whole island. I'll contact you by Codec after you reach your target.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Anyone going with me?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | As usual, this is a one-man inflitration mission.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Weapons and equipment OSP (on-site procurement)?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes. This a top-secret black op. Don't expect any official support.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100003_The_chief_of_DARPA.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The Chief of DARPA and the president of an arms manufacturing company... what business did they have at a nuclear weapons disposal facility?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The truth is that secret exercises were being conducted at the time the terrorist group attacked.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Must be extremely important exercises if those two were directly involved. Were they testing some kind of new advanced weapon?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm not privy to that information.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Do we know exactly where they're being held?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The DARPA chief has also been injected with a mini-transmitter. As you get closer you should be able to pick up his location on your radar.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100004_Do_they_really_have_the_ability_to_launch_a_nuclear_missile.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Do they really have the ability to launch a nuclear missile?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | They say they do. They even gave us the serial number of the warhead they plan to use.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Was the number confirmed?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm afraid so. At the very least, they've got their hands on a real nuclear warhead.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Isn't there some kind of safety device to prevent this kind of terrorism?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes. Every missile and warhead in our arsenal is equipped with a PAL, which uses a discreet detonation code.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | PAL?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Permissive Action Link. A safety control system built into all nuclear weapons systems. But even so, we can't rest easy.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Why not?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Because the DARPA Chief knows the detonation code.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | But even if they have a nuclear warhead, it must've been removed from its missile. All the missiles on these disposal sites are supposed to be dismantled. It's not that easy to get your hands on an ICBM (intercontinental ballistic missle).
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That used to be true, but since the end of the Cold War you can get anything if you have enough money and the right connections.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100005_So_what_exactly_are_they_demanding.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So what exactly are they demanding?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | A person's remains.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Remains?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That's right. To be more accurate, cell specimens which contain the individual's genomic information.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Cell specimens? Why would they want that?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The terrorists need them. You see these Next-Generation Special Forces have been strengthened through gene therapy.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Strengthened?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You've heard of the Human Genome Project. They've been mapping the human genome, and they're nearly finished. Following up on this research, the military has been working towards identifiying those genes which are responsible for making effective soldiers.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | There are genes that do that?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes, and using gene therapy they're able to transplant those genes into regular soldiers.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Gene therapy?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'll explain this part. With gene therapy, we can remove those genes which we know may lead to sickness or disease, and that the same time, splice in genes with beneficial effects such as resistance to cancer for example.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | In other words, we can overcome all sorts of genetic diseases and at the same time add genetic characteristics as desired.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Okay, and so if you knew what genes were responsible for making the perfect soldier, you could implant them in the same way, right?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes we could.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | But it all depends on being able to isolate and identify those "soldier genes".
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | And in order to do that, it's helpful to study the genomic information of one of the greatest soldiers ever.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100006_One_of_the_greatest_soldiers_ever.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | One of the greatest soldiers ever?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The man they call the greatest warrior of the twentieth century.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You don't mean Big Boss?!
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That's right. We've been working feverishly to identify the genes responsible for his incredible combat skill. So far we've discovered about sixty of the so-called "soldier genes."
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So his body was recovered after all.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes, and his cells have remained frozen in cryo-chamber. His genomic information is a priceless treasure to mankind.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Priceless to the military perhaps.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | His body was burned severely, but it was possible to restore his DNA (deoxyribonucleic acid) profile from just a single strand of his hair.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You people are amazing. And then you're going to transplant those genes into soldiers?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes. We'll use a process that I discovered called gene targeting. The strongest soldiers don't become what they are by acquiring their skills through training or experience, we now know that hereditary factors are far more crucial for creating superior soldiers.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, we can't give them his body. It's potentially more dangerous than all the warheads on that island put together.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I hear the terrorists are calling themselves the "Sons of Big Boss."
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The Sons of Big Boss.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100007_What's_the_time_limit.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What's the time limit?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | 24 hours. They say they'll launch after 24 hours.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Did they say what the target will be?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So far they haven't mentioned a target.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | When did the countdown start?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | 5 hours ago.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100008_Colonel_who_are_you_speaking_for.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Colonel, who are you speaking for?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Naturally, I'm representing the US government.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So who's in supervisory control of this operation?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The President of the United States.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Which means that the President must be meeting with his top aides in the map room about now, huh?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | No at this point they're still video conferencing with each other.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | If that's a real nuclear warhead, shouldn't they issue a COG (Continuity of Government)?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Not yet. The Secretary of Defense has operational control and is fully aware of the situation. After you infiltrate, if you determine they possess nuclear launch capabilities a COG will be issued.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Well if they haven't relocated to nuclear shelter under Mount Washingtion, I suppose there isn't that much reason to worry yet. Is the National Security Agency in on this?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes. So is the DIA, the Defense Intelligence Agency.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The DIA? I'm starting to get a bad feeling about this.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | They'll be sending us some support.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | We don't need desk jockies. We need a nuclear weapons specialist.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Of course. A nuclear weapons specialist has already been assigned to us.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100009_We_need_backup_from_a_specialist.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | We need backup from a specialist. I'm just an amateur when it comes to nuclear weapons.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I know. That's why I've requested the assistance of a military analyst named Nastasha Romanenko. She'll be providing you backup by Codec.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | A female analyst?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | She's built up an impressive record as an advisor to the Nuclear Emergency Search Team. Contact her if you have any questions. She's also an expert on hi-tech weapons.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Where's she working from?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | At her home in Los Angeles.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | California. Seems like a million miles away.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100010_How_well_armed_are_these_terrorists.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | How well-armed are these terrorists? I know there was an exercise going on at the time they revolted.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | They're heavily armed I'm afraid.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What about they're battle experience.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The six members of FOX-HOUND in charge are all hardened veterans. They're tough enough to eat nails and ask for seconds.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I wouldn't expect anything less from FOX-HOUND.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The others are Next-Generation Special Forces. They're not your average grunts either.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100011_Tell_me_about_these_Next-Generation_Special_Forces.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Tell me about these Next-Generation Special Forces.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | They started out as an anti-terrorist special-ops unit made up of members from former biochem units, technical escort units, and the Nuclear Emergency Search Team. Their purpose was to respond to threats involving next-generation weapons of mass destruction, including NBC (nuclear/biological/chemica) weapons.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Until "they" were added that is.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Who's "they"?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | These guys didn't start out as regular army.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Looks like a pretty international group. Mercenaries?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yeah. And it gets worse. Most of them were from a merc agency that I think you're familiar with. They were part of Big Boss' private guard. And after Big Boss went down, the military just bought out all their contracts.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Outer Heaven.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | After that they were merged with our own VR unit, Force 21, and re-trained. If you ask me, these so-called "Next-Generation Special Forces" should to be called "simulated soldiers." They have no real battle experience.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Video game players, huh?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Don't forget they've all been strengthened with gene therapy. They carry genes which make them excellent soldiers. Don't get careless just because they don't have much experience.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I thought using genetically modified soldiers was prohibited by international law.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes, but those are just declarations not actual treaties.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The interesting thing is that nearly every member of the unit conspired in this attack.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100012_How_could_an_entire_unit_be_subverted_to_rebellion.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | How could an entire unit be subverted to rebellion?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | They're calling it a revolution.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Since they all went through the same gene therapy, they probably felt closer than brothers. They see the unit as their only family.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The Sons of Big Boss. But if they were regular army, they must've been interviewed periodically by army counsellers.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | According to their files, they all got straight A's on their psychological tests. They all seemed like fine, upstanding patriotic soldiers.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | But they all took part in the uprising?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | No. Several people didn't show up on the day of the exercise. That's why there was a resupply of troops.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Was there any sign recently that something might be wrong?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | There was a report a month ago that they were acting strangely.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Apparently they consulted classified information about the soldier genes and performed their own gene therapy experiments.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | They can do that even without you?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Well our gene therapy process is almost completely automated. And besides that they're all geniuses with IQs over 180.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Even the existence of this genome army is a national secret of the highest order. We'd been hoping to investigate this quietly and deal with it behind closed doors.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100013_High_Tech_Special_Forces_Unit_FOX-HOUND.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Hi-Tech special forces unit FOX-HOUND. Your former unit, and one that I was a commander of. An elite group combining firepower and expertise. They're every bit as good as when I was commanding them.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | So they're still around.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | There are six members of FOX-HOUND involved in this terrorist activity. Psycho Mantis, with his powerful psychic abilities. Sniper Wolf, the beautiful and deadly sharpshooter. Decoy Octopus, master of disguise. Vulcan Raven, giant and shaman. And Revolver Ocelot, specialist in interrogation and a formidable gunfighter.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Looks like a lovely bunch of folks. Too bad we'll be meeting under these circumstances.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | And finally, in charge of them, FOX-HOUND's squad leader Liquid Snake.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Liquid Snake?!
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Yes and you're the only person who can stand against him.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100014_Liquid_Snake.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Liquid Snake.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Liquid Snake. The man with the same codename as you.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Tell me what you know.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | He fought in the Gulf War as a teenager, the youngest person in the SAS (British Special Air Service).  His job was to track down and destroy mobile SCUD missile launching platforms. You were there too I believe. Didn't you infiltrate western Iraq with a platoon of Green Berets?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I was just a kid myself back then.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The details are classified, but it seems that originally he penetrated the the Middle East as a sleeper for the SIS.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | He was a spy for the British Secret Intelligence Service?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | But he never once showed his face in Century House. He was taken prisoner in Iraq, and after that there was no trace of him for several years. After you retired, he was rescued and became a member of FOX-HOUND.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I thought that by the time I left they were no longer using codenames.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I don't know his real name. That information is so highly classified that even I can't look at it. Here's a photo of him.  Pretty shocking, huh?  His skin tone is a little different but otherwise you two are exact duplicates.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I have a twin?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I don't know the details, but it seems so. That's why we really need you for this mission.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You're the only one who can beat him. Now that I've met you, I know. You've got something he doesn't. I can see it in your eyes.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Why don't I find that thought more comforting?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100015_Colonel_I_don't_work_for_the_government_anymore.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Colonel, I don't work for the government anymore. Let me go back to Twin Lakes.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Why Snake? Is your life in Alaska all that great?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | There's a dogsled race this week. Next Saturday I have to be in Anchorage.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | The Iditarod? The longest sled race in the world? When did you become a dog musher?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Right now my fifty huskies are my only family. I've got to take care of them.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Don't worry about your dogs.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What do you mean?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm sorry Snake but this vessel is headed for the Bering Sea. There's no room for debate.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I told you, even if I do owe you I don't anything to this army or this country!
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You will accept this assignment!
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Why should I be stupid enough to do that? I'm no patriot.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, there's enough dirt in your file from your days as an agent to keep you in the stockade until you're a very old man.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Oh I see. Blackmail.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | No Snake. I prefer to look at it as helping you to come to a decision more easily. But anyway, I know you better than that. You'd take this assignment even without the threat.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Why do you say that?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You're a natural born soldier. You're not the grow old gracefully type. Same for all of us who've seen real action. The only place we can feel truly alive is on the battlefield. I'm a solider too. I know those feelings of powerlessness, frustration that you feel everyday. You've tried to play the boy scout out there in Alaska, but you can't race dogs in the snow forever.  Why don't you come back to us and be a soldier again.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You think my life is some kind of joke?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Snake, I just want to give you back your purpose in life.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100016_Colonel_you're_retired.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Colonel, you're retired. Why are you involved in this?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Becaue there aren't many people who know FOX-HOUND as well as I do.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Is that really the only reason?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I've been soldiering for a long time, I don't know anything else. I guess even though I'm getting a little old, I still love to be in the field.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Colonel, you're a lousy liar. Tell me the real reason.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Okay Snake. Sorry. I'll be frank. A person very dear to me is being held hostage.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Who is it?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | My neice. Meryl.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100017_What_was_your_niece_doing_here.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What was your niece doing here?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Several soldiers were reported missing the day of the revolt. And my niece was one of those called in as an emergency replacement.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | She looks like you.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | She's my little brother's girl. He died in the Gulf War. Since then I've been watching after her.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | A personal motive, Colonel. That's not very soldierly.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm retired. I'm just an old man now. And I'm your friend.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Since when are we friends?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I've thought of us as friends since the fall of Zanzibar.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | With my personality I don't have too many friends.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That's what I trust about you. It's what makes you human. Please Snake. Save my niece Meryl.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | All right, but I have two conditions.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Name them.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | One, no more secrets between us. I want complete disclosure at all times and two, I'll only accept orders from you, Colonel. No cutoffs involved okay?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Agreed. That's why I was called. But one thing.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I'm not a colonel anymore. Just a retired old warhorse.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I understand, Colonel.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100018_That_doctor.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That doctor. Is she part of this operation too?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-campbell
                | Campbell
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | She was in charge of FOX-HOUND's gene therapy. She knows more about those men than anyone else.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You mean you've seen them naked?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Make no mistake. I'm not a nurse. I'm a scientist.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | By the way, what was that injection for?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | It's a combination of and nanomachines and an anti-freezing peptide so that your blood and other bodily fluids don't freeze, even at sub-arctic temperatures.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Nanomachines?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Not just one kind either. There are different types which will replenish the supply of adrenaline, nutrition and sugar in your bloodstream.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Now I don't have to worry about food.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I also put some nootropics in there.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Say what?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Nootropics. It's a class of drugs which wil help improve your mental functioning.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | It'll make smarter huh? Anything else?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Benzedrine. It's a type of stimulant. It'll keep you alert and responsive for twelve straight hours.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | That was quite a cocktail. Anything else in there?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Those nanomachines will also keep your Codec's batteries charged up.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I guess I can call you when I'm ready to go on a diet.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | You're welcome.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
    .section
        audio(src="./assets/audio/cd1/vox/100019_I_need_to_borrow_your_scissors.mp3", controls="")
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I need to borrow your scissors.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | What are you going to do?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Don't worry. Just going to clean myself up a little.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog
            em.name.name-naomi
                | Naomi
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | Huh?
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
        .dialog.dialog-snake
            em.name.name-snake
                | Snake
                span :
            p.msg.msg-en
                | I don't want to be mistaken for the leader of the terrorists.
            p.msg.msg-cn
                | NULL
